items.text: APF Module – Creation of Builder group, Builder Entity and Add Project
Once you place your Cursor over APF
This Screen will appear after user click on Calculate Builder Score
Click on Add to add more rows
Click on Save to proceed ahead
Select applicable options from drop down
Click on Save & Next after entering
Click on Submit Option after documents Upload
System will generate request id and show approver’s name
Approver has to login to approve raised request
Raised Builder group approval will reflect here, click on it
Edit details which to be edit and scroll down
After editing the details click here to save the details
New Updated details will reflect here
After Clicking here Edit and delete options will
reflect, click on edit to edit the details
Edit the details and click on Save option
Request Approved Successfully message will reflect once
Once you place your Cursor over APF
This Screen will reflect after you click on Add Entity
Select applicable option from drop down
Enter name of person selected in Contact type
Click here to Upload Entity related docs
Request ID and approver name will reflect here
Approver will have to login to approve request
Pending request for approval will reflect here, click on it to Proceed ahead
This Screen will appear, check all the details
Once you place your Cursor over APF
Enter no. of Towers here , if
Enter Total no. of units here, if
Enter details if same is not
enter details if same is not
Enter PAN no. of Entity to link with this Project
Select Name of Entity to link
Click on Add new to New
Enter PAN details here if available
Click here to upload docs size more than 15 mb to 200 mb
Enter page no. here for Indexing
Click here to Save the uploaded file
APF request ID will reflect here
